    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor overall condition and being sold honestly as-is. It runs and is usable as a project, parts car, or cheap around-town beater, but it shows heavy age and wear throughout, with clear cosmetic flaws inside and out and likely deferred maintenance. Buyers should expect imperfections, possible mechanical needs, and no pretense that this is a turn-key example. Best suited for someone who wants an inexpensive vehicle and is comfortable taking on repairs.",
