    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$46,900 - Exceptionally clean, mint-condition vehicle that shows like it has been very well cared for. The exterior presents beautifully with a glossy finish and no notable cosmetic issues, and the interior is equally impressive with clean, well-kept materials and minimal to no visible wear. It feels tight, fresh, and turn-key throughout, and a buyer can expect a vehicle that stands out from typical used examples for its condition and overall presentation.",
